0 HOME~

Syntax: home

If you get stuck in a no-recall, no-gate room, you can use the home 
command at any level to take yourself to a safe room.  However, if you 
use it during battle, you lose 500 exp.  If you use it, you lose 3/4 your 
hp, 3/4 your mana, and 3/4 your moves.  It will ALWAYS work... just keep 
in mind the penalties attached to it.
~

